-- Sum of Squares -------------------------------------------------------------
Executable dph-sumsq
  Build-depends:  base == 4.4.*, vector == 0.7.*, dph-base == 0.5.*, dph-prim-par == 0.5.*, dph-par == 0.5.*, random == 1.0.*, old-time == 1.0.*
  Main-is:        Main.hs
  other-modules:  SumSquaresVector
                  SumSquaresVectorised
                  Timing Randomish
